      "author": "ppravdin",
      "description": "This update focuses on the desktop experience and tidier notes.\n\n- The floating record button now works on desktop too. Turn it on in settings, where it sits in the bottom corner near the status bar. On mobile it stays on as before.\n- Audio attaches reliably again. When you start a new voice note, the recording is saved as a playable audio file in the note. Adding more to the same note no longer stacks up extra audio players.\n- New \"New voice note\" button in the ribbon, so you can start a fresh voice note in one click.\n- Back to back dictations no longer run together. A space is added between them.\n- Notes sort more sensibly. With categories on, Work, Life and Ideas go to their folders and Misc stays in the Voice Notes root.\n",
      "downloadCount": 14,
