      "author": "ppravdin",
      "description": "Mobile recording got a lot better in this version.\n\n- New floating mic button on mobile. Recording is always one tap away. It moves up above the keyboard while you are typing and drops to the bottom corner when the keyboard is closed.\n- Clearer recording status. The mic turns red while you record and shows a spinner while your note is being transcribed, both on the toolbar button and the floating button.\n- Tapping the floating button no longer closes the keyboard, so your cursor stays where you left it.\n",
